\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Context-length scaling benchmark. (a)\nobreakspace  {}Stacked component breakdown: SFS build (grey), tsinfer + tree features (blue), and model forward pass (orange). (b)\nobreakspace  {}Forward pass only: both models complete in ${\sim }16$\,ms regardless of context length, confirming Mamba's $O(L)$ scaling.}}{11}{figure.4}\protected@file@percent }
